groupdocs_annotation_for_net.description: This extension allows you to integrate the downloadable .NET version of the GroupDocs.Annotation into TYPO3 CMS. Once installed, you will be able to display over 50 types of documents and images along with an annotation toolbar on any page within your TYPO3 website. Supported file formats include: PDF, Microsoft Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Visio, Outlook, Project, OpenDocument, AutoCAD and raster images. Among key benefits of the GroupDocs.Annotation for .NET are: 1. Documents embedded to your website can be viewed and annotated from any web-enabled device and using any standard web-browser. Your website visitors dont have to install any office software or browser plugins. 2. A comprehensive set of annotation tools, including: sticky notes, rectangles, polyline, arrows, watermarks, redaction, text underline/strikethrough and ruler. 3. Several users can review and annotate the same document simultaneously, each seeing others comments in real time. 4. Documents annotated online on your website can then be exported to a PDF file or printed out with annotations in them. 5. Thanks to the built-in Digital Rights Management feature, you can prevent users from copying, downloading and printing the documents you share on your website. Please note that this plugin requires the GroupDocs.Annotation for .NET library to be installed on your server first. You can download a free evaluation copy of the library from the GroupDocs website: https://groupdocs.com/dot-net/document-annotation-library

groupdocs_assembly.description: The GroupDocs.Assembly for Cloud plugin for Typo3 CMS allows you to embed questionnaire forms in a website to easily collect information from users.

groupdocs_comparison.description: The GroupDocs.Comparison for Cloud plugin for Typo3 CMS allows you to embed and compare two Word documents, as well as PDF files and Excel spreadsheets, from within your website.

groupdocs_viewer.description: The GroupDocs.Viewer for Cloud plugin for Typo3 CMS helps you embed documents, complete with GroupDocs high-fidelity, online document viewer, into webpages to view documents of many different file formats.

groupdocs_viewer_for_dotnet.description: This extension allows you to integrate the downloadable .NET version of the GroupDocs.Viewer into TYPO3 CMS. Once installed, you will be able to embed and display over 50 types of documents and images on any page within your TYPO3 website. Supported file formats include: PDF, Microsoft Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Visio, Outlook, Project, OpenDocument, AutoCAD and raster images. Among key benefits of the GroupDocs.Viewer are: 1. Clear native text rendering (users can select/copy text right from documents embedded to a web-page); 2. Cross-browser support; 3. Users can view documents without having to install any software or plugins; 4. Convenient UI for seamless navigation of large documents in a web-browser. Please note that this plugin requires the GroupDocs.Viewer for .NET library to be installed on your server first. You can download a free evaluation copy of the library from the GroupDocs website: http://groupdocs.com/dot-net/document-viewer-library

groupdocs_viewer_for_java.description: This extension allows you to integrate the downloadable Java version of the GroupDocs.Viewer into TYPO3 CMS. Supported file formats include: PDF, Microsoft Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Visio, Outlook, Project, OpenDocument, AutoCAD and raster images. Some of the key benefits of the GroupDocs.Viewer are: 1.
